			<IDXSKIP>This entry was posted in </IDXSKIP><IDXSKIP><a href="http://svetlanaignatovich.com/category/articles/" title="Просмотреть все записи в рубрике &laquo;Статьи&raquo;" rel="category tag">Статьи</a></IDXSKIP> and tagged <a href="http://svetlanaignatovich.com/tag/vybor-nishi/" rel="tag">Выбор ниши</a>, <a href="http://svetlanaignatovich.com/tag/nisha/" rel="tag">Ниша</a> on <a href="http://svetlanaignatovich.com/pribylnaya-ideya-dlya-biznesa/" title="13:04" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-10-30T13:04:21+00:00">30.10.2015</time></a><IDXSKIP><span class="by-author"> by </IDXSKIP><IDXSKIP><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://svetlanaignatovich.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a></span></IDXSKIP></span><IDXSKIP>.								</IDXSKIP></footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
